Package: com.zeshan.phoneaura
Name: PhoneAura
Version: 0.4.1
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Description: RootHide registration and full-surface release for the iOS 16 Phone app. Includes a visible PhoneAura Studio Home Screen app, a repaired PreferenceLoader Settings pane, complete custom Favorites, Recents, Contacts and Keypad surfaces, selectable favorite contacts, adaptive call-history and Contacts data, and safe stock detail and in-call navigation.
